Update User Guide (Group commands under Data classication and management)
Refactor Tag Class. Change Tag class to an interface. Add Default Enum, DefaultTag, TagList and UserTag.
Change exception in TagList Add CreateTagCommand
Basic refactoring of Person and AddressBook classes to StudyPlan and ModulePlanner. Still have occurrences of Person in classes that are not intended to be used.
More refactoring of Person and Address Book classes. Delete Name, Email, Address, Phone classes under package person and delete corresponding test classes.
Add UniqueTagList class, which also has a hashmap linking the tag names to the actual tags.
Update UG to include extra default tags.
Add temporary holder CommandResult for execute method. Needs to be implemented.
Create more tag-related exceptions Add AddTagCommand
Add tag commands to (1) view all tags, (2) view default tags, (3) view modules with specific tags, (4) view tags of a specific module
Contains reverted changes to tag commands and exceptions
Modify user guide to match changes in DefaultTagType
Update StudyPlan constructor (assign default tags - incomplete) Still have to add core, ue, ulr tags
Fix all checkstyle issues including in tests
Made slight modifications to tag-related commands and classes
Modify InvalidTagNameException to take in a message instead of having a fixed message
Add UserTag test and TagBuilder to be used for tests
Modify tag parser and modify CreateTagCommand and TagModuleCommand to work with corresponding parsers
Remove module code checking within commands and added RemoveTagModuleCommand and ViewModuleTagsCommand to ModulePlannerParser
Change UniqueTagList to check whether a tag with a given tag name is in the list and allow getting of tags using tag names. Add DeleteTagCommand
Add DefaultTagTest, UniqueTagListTest Modify commands based on modification to uniqueTagList implementation

Implement initial assigning of Completed DefaultTag to the study plan. Modify StudyPlan constructor to take in current semester Modify SetCurrentSemesterCommand to update modules in previous semesters to have completed tags
Update UG Remove commands to view total completed mcs and prereq. Move validmods command to Verification section
Change implemention of previous tagging-related commands to minimise accessing methods of other classes aside from model.
Update implementation for assigning of completed tags when a new currentsemester is set. Takes into account setting an earlier current semester (completed tags for later semesters are removed)
Edit implementation for RenameTagCommand (not yet in Parser)
Modify checking and usage of tag names to be case insensitive
Add enum class for types of result displays on left panel of GUI
Update GUI to show command results as tag list and others (commented out)
Update Development Guide with implementation details for Tagging Module Feature
